OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,FA tree servicing company has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to breaching safety regulations
OL,8,Fafter one of its workers nearly died
OL,9,Ffrom an electric shock while carrying
OL,10,Fout hedge maintenance in the dark.
OL,12,FCCTV footage shows the moment Joshua
OL,13,FPocknell was struck on the busy A3102
OL,14,Fnear Royal Wootton Bassett, just
OL,15,Fbefore midnight on 19 January 2024,
OL,16,Fwhen the mobile lighting tower he was
OL,17,Fpushing made contact with an 11,000-
OL,18,Fvolt overhead power line.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
