FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,FHe was rushed to hospital with life-
OL,7,Fthreatening injuries, and later
OL,8,Fdiscovered a bone-deep hole had burned
OL,9,Fthrough his arm and hip.
OL,11,FMore than two years after the
OL,12,Fincident, the 26-year-old says he's
OL,13,Fhad his life 'torn from beneath him'.
OL,15,FDescribing the moment the lighting
OL,16,Ftower hit the overhead power lines,
OL,17,FJoshua said: "I couldn't let go of it.
OL,18,FMy whole body locked, and I felt hot
OL,19,Fand cramping.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,F"I could hear the electricity in my
OL,7,Fhead and thought I was going to die. I
OL,8,Fhit the floor and passed out, still
OL,9,Fcramping.
OL,11,F"I later discovered a hole had burned
OL,12,Fthrough my arm and hip all the way to
OL,13,Fthe bone."
OL,15,F"My injuries were complex and
OL,16,Fchallenging, and there were five or
OL,17,Fsix different surgeons involved in my
OL,18,Ftreatment. I still experience
OL,19,Fconsiderable pain and strange bodily
OL,20,Fsensations, including nerve pain and
OL,21,Fitching.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@JO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,F"This incident has torn the life from
OL,7,Fbeneath me, and I don't think I will
OL,8,Fbe able to return to the job that I
OL,9,Fused to love."
OL,11,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,12,Finvestigation found Joshua's employer,
OL,13,FUpton Specialist Tree Services, had
OL,14,Frequested a Wiltshire Council permit
OL,15,Fto carry out the work at night;
OL,16,Fhowever, it had failed to plan for, or
OL,17,Frisk assess the dangers posed by
OL,18,Foverhead power lines.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,FHSE inspector Tom Preston said:
OL,7,F"Joshua is lucky to be alive. Overhead
OL,8,Felectrical power lines present extreme
OL,9,Frisks to workers, but the risks can
OL,10,Fand must be controlled.
OL,12,F"Work near overhead power lines should
OL,13,Fonly be carried out where it can be
OL,14,Fdone safely, following a suitable risk
OL,15,Fassessment, the use of barriers or
OL,16,Fsafety zones, and proper training on
OL,17,Fthe equipment being used.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,F"In this case, a worker sustained
OL,7,Fsevere injuries in a traumatic
OL,8,Fincident for all concerned that was
OL,9,Fentirely preventable.
OL,11,F"HSE will take action against those
OL,12,Fwho fail to take the steps necessary
OL,13,Fto protect people at work."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
