PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777978995
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment tree surgeon
OL,4,Celectrocuted by 11,000 volt power line
OL,6,FDorset-based Upton Specialised Tree
OL,7,FServices Ltd, pleaded guilty to the
OL,8,Fcharge of breaching Regulation 14 of
OL,9,Fthe Electricity at Work Regulations
OL,10,F1989 by virtue of Regulation 3. It was
OL,11,Ffined #60,000 on Friday 1 May and
OL,12,Fordered to pay #6,237 in costs at
OL,13,FBristol Magistrates' Court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
